network-manager-applet: network-manager-applet (Panel Applet for NetworkManager)
network-manager-applet:
network-manager-applet: NetworkManager attempts to make networking invisible. When moving 
network-manager-applet: into areas you've been before, NetworkManager automatically connects 
network-manager-applet: to the last network the user chose to connect to. Likewise, when 
network-manager-applet: back at the desk, NetworkManager will switch to the faster, more 
network-manager-applet: reliable wired network connection. 
network-manager-applet: 
network-manager-applet: This package contains a GNOME Panel applet to easily control 
network-manager-applet: NetworkManager from the desktop.
network-manager-applet: 
